        "text": "示每咒罵的時候，這樣說：“你這流人血的人啊，滾開！你這無賴啊，滾開！"
      },
      "cunp": {
        "version_id": "CUNP",
        "version_name": "和合本新標點（神版）",
        "lang": "cht",
        "text": "示每咒罵說：「你這流人血的壞人哪，去吧去吧！"
      },
      "nasb": {
        "version_id": "NASB",
        "version_name": "New American Standard Bible",
        "lang": "en",
        "text": "Thus Shimei said when he cursed, “Get out, get out, you man of bloodshed, and worthless fellow!"
      },
      "niv": {
        "version_id": "NIV",
        "version_name": "New International Version",
        "lang": "en",
        "text": "As he cursed, Shimei said, “Get out, get out, you murderer, you scoundrel!"
      },
      "nlt": {
        "version_id": "NLT",
        "version_name": "New Living Translation",
        "lang": "en",
        "text": "“Get out of here, you murderer, you scoundrel!” he shouted at David."
      }
